thothbot.parallax.core.shared.geometries

Class TubeGeometry

  • java.lang.Object
    • thothbot.parallax.core.client.renderers.WebGLGeometry
      • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.core.AbstractGeometry
        • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.core.Geometry
          • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.geometries.TubeGeometry

  • public final class TubeGeometry
extends Geometry
    Creates a tube which extrudes along a 3d spline.

    Uses parallel transport frames as described in http://www.cs.indiana.edu

    Based on the three.js code.

    Author:
    thothbot
